data.description: Step into this exquisite property with its warm knotty pine custom cabinets and stunning finishes throughout. The layout is simply captivating, boasting a spacious laundry room complete with a sink, built-ins, and ample storage for hang-ups and hunting gear. Discover the custom office space, perfectly tucked away with its built-in desk and hutch. Prepare to be amazed by the unparalleled custom kitchen, featuring a farmhouse sink, a granite island with abundant seating, and a pantry with enough space to accommodate your every need. Vaulted ceilings grace the entire living area, while built-in bookshelves elegantly display your treasured trophies and mementos. The children's bedrooms offer generous closets, and the master bath serves as a serene retreat. Porcelain tile floors, resembling wood, require minimal maintenance and effortlessly sparkle with a simple mop. Prepare to be astounded by the master closet, which goes beyond expectations with its wardrobe and shoe racks reaching the ceiling. The property itself is enhanced by beautiful trees that frame the driveway, leading to an oversized garage spanning 556 sq ft. Perfectly accommodating those large SUVs with room to spare.  This can be a garden spot for those who the time to create their beds, with an acre, you have plenty of room to Add a Shop or a pool, just minutes to the Spring Market, or any school events, yet this road is a quiet place to call home. If you want to live in the Country and hoped for New Construction, this is your destination since it was built in 2021. Check us out, you will fall in Love.
